			<h3>Installation instructions</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Install the Jboss 4.2.3 server</li>
				<li>Unzip the PubMan release file to a directory</li>
				<li>
					Copy the PubMan ear to the jboss
					<i>deploy</i>
					directory
				</li>
				<li>
					Copy the
					<i>validation-ds.xml</i>
					file to the jboss
					<i>deploy</i>
					directory
				</li>
				<li>
					Copy the
					<i>pubman.properties</i>
					file to the jboss
					<i>conf</i>
					directory
				</li>
				<li>
					Now open the file
					<i>pubman.properties</i>
					and change the config settings to your needs
				</li>
				<li>
					Open the file
					<i>properties-service.xml</i>
					in the jboss
					<i>deploy</i>
					directory and add the following entry:
				</li>
				<source>
			&lt;server&gt; 
					... 
					&lt;attribute name="Properties"&gt; pubman.properties.file=./pubman.properties
					com.sun.xml.namespace.QName.useCompatibleSerialVersionUID=1.0 
					&lt;/attribute&gt; 
					... 
			&lt;/server&gt;
				</source>
				<li>
					Start the jboss server and PubMan should be available at
					<i>jboss_server_url</i>
					/pubman
				</li>
			</ul>

